#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.elliprg.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.elliprg"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:1 of
msgid "Completely-symmetric elliptic integral of the second kind."
msgstr "第二类完全对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:3 of
msgid "The function RG is defined as [1]_"
msgstr "RG 函数定义如下 [1]_"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:5 of
msgid ""
"R_{\\mathrm{G}}(x, y, z) =\n"
"   \\frac{1}{4} \\int_0^{+\\infty} [(t + x) (t + y) (t + z)]^{-1/2}\n"
"   \\left(\\frac{x}{t + x} + \\frac{y}{t + y} + \\frac{z}{t + z}\\right) "
"t\n"
"   dt"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.elliprg.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:12
#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:15
#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:18 of
msgid ""
"Real or complex input parameters. `x`, `y`, or `z` can be any number in "
"the complex plane cut along the negative real axis."
msgstr ""
"实数或复数输入参数。`x`、`y` 或 `z` 可以是沿负实轴切割的复平面上的任意"
"数字。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:21 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function values"
msgstr "函数值的可选输出数组"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.elliprg.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:24 of
msgid ""
"**R** -- Value of the integral. If all of `x`, `y`, and `z` are real, the"
" return value is real. Otherwise, the return value is complex."
msgstr ""
"**R** -- 积分值。如果 `x`、`y` 和 `z` 都是实数，则返回值为实数；否则"
"返回值为复数。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.elliprg.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:30 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:31 of
msgid "Degenerate symmetric integral."
msgstr "退化对称积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprd`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:34 of
msgid "Symmetric elliptic integral of the second kind."
msgstr "第二类对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:36 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprf`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:37 of
msgid "Completely-symmetric elliptic integral of the first kind."
msgstr "第一类完全对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:39 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprj`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:40 of
msgid "Symmetric elliptic integral of the third kind."
msgstr "第三类对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:43 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:44 of
msgid "The implementation uses the relation [1]_"
msgstr "实现使用如下关系式 [1]_"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:46 of
msgid ""
"2 R_{\\mathrm{G}}(x, y, z) =\n"
"   z R_{\\mathrm{F}}(x, y, z) -\n"
"   \\frac{1}{3} (x - z) (y - z) R_{\\mathrm{D}}(x, y, z) +\n"
"   \\sqrt{\\frac{x y}{z}}"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:53 of
msgid ""
"and the symmetry of `x`, `y`, `z` when at least one non-zero parameter "
"can be chosen as the pivot. When one of the arguments is close to zero, "
"the AGM method is applied instead. Other special cases are computed "
"following Ref. [2]_"
msgstr ""
"以及当至少有一个非零参数可以选作主元时，`x`、`y`、`z` 的对称性。当其中"
"一个参数接近零时，改用 AGM 方法计算。其他特殊情况依据文献 [2]_ 进行计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:59 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:60 of
msgid ""
"B. C. Carlson, \"Numerical computation of real or complex elliptic "
"integrals,\" Numer. Algorithm, vol. 10, no. 1, pp. 13-26, 1995. "
"https://arxiv.org/abs/math/9409227 https://doi.org/10.1007/BF02198293"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprg:64 of
msgid ""
"B. C. Carlson, ed., Chapter 19 in \"Digital Library of Mathematical "
"Functions,\" NIST, US Dept. of Commerce. https://dlmf.nist.gov/19.16.E1 "
"https://dlmf.nist.gov/19.20.ii"
msgstr ""

